{
  "video_id": "wOsQKjNoHmw",
  "title": "Refugees want empowerment, not handouts | Robert Hakiza",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 12809.0,
      "end_time": 17905.0,
      "text": "Currently, most refugees live in the cities"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 17929.0,
      "end_time": 20128.0,
      "text": "rather than in the refugee camps."
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 22133.0,
      "end_time": 25958.0,
      "text": "We represent over 60 percent"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 25982.0,
      "end_time": 29730.0,
      "text": "of the number of refugees globally."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 31442.0,
      "end_time": 35233.0,
      "text": "With the majority of refugees living in urban areas,"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 36617.0,
      "end_time": 40982.0,
      "text": "there is a strong need for a paradigm shift and new thinking."
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 43363.0,
      "end_time": 47986.0,
      "text": "Rather than wasting money on building walls,"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 49668.0,
      "end_time": 53688.0,
      "text": "it would be better to spend on programs"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 53712.0,
      "end_time": 55970.0,
      "text": "to help refugees to help themselves."
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 55994.0,
      "end_time": 61997.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 62736.0,
      "end_time": 67759.0,
      "text": "We always have to leave behind all our possessions."
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 68940.0,
      "end_time": 71730.0,
      "text": "But not our skills and knowledge."
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 73352.0,
      "end_time": 76716.0,
      "text": "If allowed to live a productive life,"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 77641.0,
      "end_time": 80585.0,
      "text": "refugees can help themselves"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 80609.0,
      "end_time": 84274.0,
      "text": "and contribute to the development of their host country."
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 86748.0,
      "end_time": 89858.0,
      "text": "I was born in the city called Bukavu,"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 89882.0,
      "end_time": 91683.0,
      "text": "South Kivu,"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 91707.0,
      "end_time": 94680.0,
      "text": "in the Democratic Republic of Congo."
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 95359.0,
      "end_time": 98895.0,
      "text": "I am the fifth-born in a family of 12 children."
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 100723.0,
      "end_time": 104891.0,
      "text": "My father, a mechanic by profession,"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 104915.0,
      "end_time": 107680.0,
      "text": "worked very hard to send me to school."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 109320.0,
      "end_time": 111908.0,
      "text": "Just like other young people,"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 112995.0,
      "end_time": 115288.0,
      "text": "I had a lot of plans and dreams."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 116756.0,
      "end_time": 118870.0,
      "text": "I wanted to complete my studies,"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 119616.0,
      "end_time": 120948.0,
      "text": "get a nice job,"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 121554.0,
      "end_time": 124331.0,
      "text": "marry and have my own children"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 124355.0,
      "end_time": 125822.0,
      "text": "and support my family."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 127124.0,
      "end_time": 129434.0,
      "text": "But this didn&#39;t happen."
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 131871.0,
      "end_time": 138522.0,
      "text": "War in my homeland forced me to flee to Uganda in 2008,"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 138546.0,
      "end_time": 140353.0,
      "text": "nine years ago."
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 142850.0,
      "end_time": 147276.0,
      "text": "My family joined a steady exodus of refugees"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 147300.0,
      "end_time": 150520.0,
      "text": "who settled in Uganda&#39;s capital, Kampala."
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 152147.0,
      "end_time": 153593.0,
      "text": "In my country,"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 155380.0,
      "end_time": 156815.0,
      "text": "I lived already in the city,"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 157839.0,
      "end_time": 162591.0,
      "text": "and we felt Kampala was much better than a refugee camp."
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 166460.0,
      "end_time": 168696.0,
      "text": "Refugees in the cities"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 168720.0,
      "end_time": 172616.0,
      "text": "have always been denied international assistance,"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 174322.0,
      "end_time": 179701.0,
      "text": "even after their recognition by UNHCR in 1997."
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 181157.0,
      "end_time": 187442.0,
      "text": "In addition to the poverty problem we were confronted with"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 187466.0,
      "end_time": 189467.0,
      "text": "as the local urban poor,"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 190546.0,
      "end_time": 194275.0,
      "text": "we were facing challenges due to our refugee status,"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 194299.0,
      "end_time": 196386.0,
      "text": "such as a language barrier."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 197315.0,
      "end_time": 200766.0,
      "text": "In Congo, the official language is French."
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 201592.0,
      "end_time": 204234.0,
      "text": "But in Uganda, it is English."
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 205282.0,
      "end_time": 208416.0,
      "text": "We didn&#39;t have access to education and health."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 209427.0,
      "end_time": 213410.0,
      "text": "We were exposed to harassment,"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 213434.0,
      "end_time": 217495.0,
      "text": "exploitation, intimidation and discrimination."
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 219308.0,
      "end_time": 223439.0,
      "text": "Humanitarian organizations mostly focused"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 223463.0,
      "end_time": 226218.0,
      "text": "on the formal settlement in rural areas,"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 226998.0,
      "end_time": 229779.0,
      "text": "and there was nothing in place for us."
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 232529.0,
      "end_time": 235266.0,
      "text": "But we didn&#39;t want handouts."
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 236148.0,
      "end_time": 239108.0,
      "text": "We wanted to work and support ourselves."
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 240752.0,
      "end_time": 244690.0,
      "text": "I joined my other two colleagues in exile"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 244930.0,
      "end_time": 247210.0,
      "text": "and set up an organization to support other refugees."
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 248655.0,
      "end_time": 253268.0,
      "text": "YARID -- Young African Refugees for Integral Development --"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 253935.0,
      "end_time": 257991.0,
      "text": "began as a conversation within the Congolese community."
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 259584.0,
      "end_time": 261743.0,
      "text": "We asked the community"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 261767.0,
      "end_time": 266102.0,
      "text": "how they could organize themselves to solve these challenges."
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 267514.0,
      "end_time": 271737.0,
      "text": "The YARID programs for support evolve in stages,"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 272750.0,
      "end_time": 277624.0,
      "text": "progressing from soccer community, to English language"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 277648.0,
      "end_time": 279965.0,
      "text": "to sewing livelihoods."
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 281655.0,
      "end_time": 286244.0,
      "text": "The soccer changed the energy"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 286269.0,
      "end_time": 288569.0,
      "text": "of unemployed youth"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 288593.0,
      "end_time": 292310.0,
      "text": "and connected people from different communities."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 293173.0,
      "end_time": 295260.0,
      "text": "The free English classes"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 295284.0,
      "end_time": 299791.0,
      "text": "help empower people to engage with the Ugandan community,"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 299815.0,
      "end_time": 303974.0,
      "text": "allowing them to get to know their neighbors and sell wares."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 305584.0,
      "end_time": 310982.0,
      "text": "The vocational training program offers livelihood skills,"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 311600.0,
      "end_time": 315433.0,
      "text": "and with them, important opportunities for economic self-reliance."
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 316101.0,
      "end_time": 320204.0,
      "text": "We&#39;ve seen so many families"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 320228.0,
      "end_time": 322680.0,
      "text": "become self-sustaining."
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 323698.0,
      "end_time": 326835.0,
      "text": "We&#39;ve seen who no longer needs our help."
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 328690.0,
      "end_time": 332892.0,
      "text": "As YARID&#39;s programs have expanded,"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 333720.0,
      "end_time": 337914.0,
      "text": "it has included an increasing range of nationalities --"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 339930.0,
      "end_time": 343710.0,
      "text": "Congolese, Rwandan, Burundian,"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 343942.0,
      "end_time": 346482.0,
      "text": "Somalis, Ethiopian, South Sudanese."
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 347347.0,
      "end_time": 352930.0,
      "text": "Today, YARID has supported over 3,000 refugees across Kampala"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 353671.0,
      "end_time": 355325.0,
      "text": "and continues supporting more."
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 355350.0,
      "end_time": 359950.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 359974.0,
      "end_time": 365410.0,
      "text": "Refugees want empowerment, not handouts."
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 366600.0,
      "end_time": 368965.0,
      "text": "We know our community better than anyone."
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 370173.0,
      "end_time": 374998.0,
      "text": "We understand the challenges and opportunities we face"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 375220.0,
      "end_time": 376555.0,
      "text": "to become self-reliant."
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 377683.0,
      "end_time": 380579.0,
      "text": "I know better than anyone"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 380603.0,
      "end_time": 384126.0,
      "text": "that initiatives created by refugees work."
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 384770.0,
      "end_time": 388637.0,
      "text": "They need to be internationally recognized and supported."
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 389624.0,
      "end_time": 392451.0,
      "text": "Give us the support we deserve,"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 392475.0,
      "end_time": 394855.0,
      "text": "and we will pay you back with interest."
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 394879.0,
      "end_time": 396219.0,
      "text": "Thank you so much."
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 396243.0,
      "end_time": 403460.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}